These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, cat, pony
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, dancing, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, dancer, entrepreneur, security-guard
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, mauve, pink, grey
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, techno, trance
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dunhill, blend, pall-mall
4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, scrabble, go
 1. the owner of the turtle is the person who likes azure##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 4. the dancer is on the far right##1
 5. the dancer is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the goat##1
 7. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 8. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the person playing go is the fan of salsa##1
10. the person playing poker is on the right of the chef##1
11. the cain-smoker is the owner of the goat##1
12. the person playing poker is the fan of techno##1
13. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
14. the dunhill-smoker is the owner of the pony##1
15. the pall-mall-smoker is the entrepreneur##1
16. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the chef##1
17. the owner of the cat is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Pet      | turtle       | pony      | cat       | goat    |
| Hobby         | board-games    | puzzles    | cooking      | dancing    |
| Job           | security-guard | chef       | entrepreneur | dancer     |
| Color   | azure         | pink  | grey      | mauve     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa          | trance     | techno       | electronic |
| Cigar         | blend       | dunhill | pall-mall       | cain   |
| Game     | go     | scrabble  | poker         | backgammon   |

