.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, garlic, peas, strawberry
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, lemonade, 7up
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, january, june, december
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, folk, soul
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, aristoff, baccarat, davidoff
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold, dahlia, orchid
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, roller, trike
 1. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 3. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 4. the fan of folk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the fan of soul is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the havana-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
13. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
14. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
15. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
16. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
17. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
| Food          | peas     | garlic     | cherry      | strawberry  |
| Beverage         | 7up  | almond-milk  | lemonade      | tea |
| Birthday   | december   | june     | october | january        |
