.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, polish, spanish
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, fishing, singing
4 different games are played: bridge, go, domino, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, horror, time-travel
House: farmhouse, tower, ranch-style, art-deco
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, lizard, rat
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, chestnut, yellow, grey
 1. the person who likes blue is on the right of the chinese##1
 2. the chinese is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the farmhouse house is the chinese##1
 4. the brazilian is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 9. the tower house is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the rat is the person watching epic movies##1
11. the person playing go is the brazilian##1
12. the spanish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
13. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
14. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is the art-deco house##1
16. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
17. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |     3     |      4      |
| Nationality          | polish          | spanish        | chinese      | brazilian      |
| Hobby         | singing       | fishing       | baking    | board-games |
| Game           | domino        | bridge     | monopoly | go        |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | time-travel   | epic      | comedy      |
| House   | tower         | ranch-style          | farmhouse       | art-deco      |
| Pet           | chinchilla    | cat           | rat       | lizard      |
| Color         | chestnut | grey | yellow   | blue      |

